name: Unicorn (Azur Lane) LoRA
description:
Unicorn (Azur Lane) LoRA

This is a LoRA, this mean that you need to update Voldy/AUTOMATIC1111's webui to use it (use git pull) .

That LoRA does not have a particular trigger (except the default <lora:LoRaName:1>).

Update 09/02/2023:

Added a WD1.4/SD2.1 version

Weight:

I only tested it at weight 1.0 but I think that lowering the weight can make it more flexible.

Recommended prompt:

That LoRA can reproduice some of her skins.

Default Skin:

single_side_bun, hair_bun,single_hair_bun , unicorn_(azur_lane),  white_dress,  white_pantyhose,   halter_dress,dress_bow, black_bow,  criss-cross_halter, detached_sleeves,   side cutout,

I also recomand to put tight_dress,see-through dress as a negative prompt if you don't want those elements.

The Gift of Spring (China dress):

china dress, white_dress, white_thighhighs, wrist_cuffs, wristband, side_slit, unicorn_(the_gift_of_spring)_(azur_lane),bun_cover,double_bun,hair_bun, cleavage_cutout, chinese clothes

A Dream of Pure Vows (wedding dress) :

unicorn_(a_dream_of_pure_vows)_(azur_lane), wedding dress, off-shoulder_dress, dress_bow,  white_choker, white_dress, white_pantyhose, strapless_dress, black_bow, dress_bow, one_side_up, single_side_bun, hair_bun,single_hair_bun,detached_sleeves,frilled_choker

Long-Awaited Date (school uniform) :

twintails, white_cardigan, white_pantyhose, white_shirt, x_hair_ornament,  school_uniform, scrunchie, serafuku,  low_twintails, black_sailor_collar, black_scrunchie, black_skirt, unicorn_(long-awaited_date)_(azur_lane), anchor symbol

Icy-Sweet Storytime (hair down + sundress + hair bow ) :

I had not initially planned to do that skin because I thought it only had 2-3 arts of it but when I went to look for image of her default skins (on booru sites) I noticed that there were many more (a dozen more) but thoses images were not properly tagged. So I decided to tags them and I used them since it would be a waste to re-tags them (on booru site) to not use them.

white_dress,  sundress, hair_bow, waist_bow,white_camisole, white_thighhighs,sleeveless_dress, zettai_ryouiki, (hair_down), bare_shoulders,  unicorn_(icy-sweet_storytime)_(azur_lane)

And see-through dress as negative prompt

Unfortunatelly it only work well on NAI and you have to use a bunch of negative prompt if you want to get a more accurate result on AnythingV4.5:

frilled choker, frilled collar,criss-cross halter,see-through, side_cutout, dress_bow,

(I wonder if I should make a anythingV3 version)

Model used for the example:

AnythingV4.5 and NAI .

That character is owned by Manjuu Games and Yostar.

modelVersions.name: V2 NAI
modelVersions.description:
Training settings:

147 images
8 repeats 
6 epochs
7056 steps (batch size:1)
Learning rate: 1e-4
Text encoder learning rate: 5e-5 
Unet learning rate: 1e-4 
max bucket resolution: 512 
clip skip: 2 
dim/alpha: 160 
batch size=1 
Base model: NAI, this mean that this LoRA work on any model derived from that particular model like AnythingV3/4/4.5, Pastel Mix, AOM 1/2,etc...
